channel.title: My new Development
channel.description:
Hey guys since i just released my little edits from demisepking v5 giving the right amount of credits with it, people liked it and said it was not bad for a beginner. So what i am now going to do is go a step further. Im going to use a cleaned version of deltascape which was provided by Chozen Pkz.
By doing this I hope to enhance my skill in creating servers since I only know very basic stuff. I will release everything I do so i get some views and feedback on how im doing.
There is alo a small request I am going to ask here as well. If anyone knows a lot of delta coding please PM me your email address so you can help me out with my development and teach me. Don't worry I will give you credits for when i release :P
[u]Features[/u]
None At the moment.
[u]Pictures[/u]
None At the moment
I hope to do well in this project as I have been told that I always pick unique places for everything. 0.0 I take the as critizism :P
